UBS’s Securities Unit Loss Ranks Among Industry’s Biggest Trading Debacles

-- B y   J o n   M e n o n
-- 
2011-09-16T05:26:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/ubs-s-securities-unit-loss-ranks-among-biggest-trading-debacles.html
UBS AG (UBSN) , Switzerland’s-biggest bank,
disclosed one of the largest trading losses after discovering
unauthorized dealing at its investment bank.  UBS said yesterday in a statement that it may be
unprofitable in the third quarter after a $2 billion loss in its
securities division. UBS didn’t identify the trader and said the
matter is still being investigated.  Following is a timeline of previous losses.  
